  {
    "key": "2acada777277b3a8bb6bae82c1495dc7e8e36ebd38854c5c149f109c4a1739f8",
    "original": "We need a battle standard so that we're recognized from afar!\nHaving one be made is costly, so we shall gather 2,000 crowns for this.",
